			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "loadlevel SCL_Main_A ; goto 833 -47 -25\r\nThe Chosen Three cinematic will play first and set up some important stuff.\r\nIn order for this dialog to trigger, Ketheric must be defeated and the Crown Controller ring must be picked up from his body.\r\nDebug command: \"oe KethericShowdown_Start\" then \"oe KethericShowdown_Defeat\" then loot the Crown Controller ring off Ketheric's body."
				},
