				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "This dialog plays after picking up the Crown Controller ring off Ketheric’s body. The player will realize that they need to collect the other two Crown Controllers from Orin and Gortash before they can use them to command the Elder Brain. Picking up the Crown Controller allows the party to continue onward to the epilogue/intermezzo of Act 2."
				}
			}
